      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for Class II device under medium model influence.",
      "rationale": "Use error assessment is outside the scope of the current credibility plan at MRL 2. No structured evaluation performed; factor scoped out per project credibility plan section 4.2."
    },
    {
