      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 given use of standardized blood analog fluid and controlled in vitro loop.",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization beyond viscosity matching is not required at the current model risk level. Factor not assessed per credibility plan."
    },
