      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Key dimensionless parameters (Reynolds number, flow coefficient) match between validation experiment and COU within 10%.",
      "rationale": "Reynolds number and flow coefficient computed for both validation and COU operating conditions. Maximum deviation of 4.7% across the five operating points. Equivalency confirmed; achieved level exceeds requirement."
