    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU1 is accepted. Eleven of thirteen factors were formally assessed; two factors (Use error, Test samples) are not assessed and are acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device under medium model influence. All assessed factors with documented required and achieved levels meet or exceed their required gradation. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the defined context of use.",
